# Universe snapshots — written locally during source runs for inspection,
# but at full scale (Afternic has ~7M rows / 360MB) they exceed GitHub's
# 100MB file limit. Universe data lands in Supabase directly via each
# source's own Supabase upsert call, not via a committed state file.
state/**/universe_snapshot.json
